Jesus atarityWen Jesus don seh aala demya tingz, di paila pipl wehn uova sopraiz bout di wie ihn tiich,
bikaaz ihn neva deh taak laik dehn tiicha a di Laa dem. Insida dat, Jesus wende tiich dem laik him dah wehn sombady weh gat plenty atarity.
Jesus kyuor wan man wid bad skin siknis niem “leprosy”<TS3>(<a href="tw://bible.*?41.1.40-45">Mark 1.40-45</a>; <a href="tw://bible.*?42.5.12-16">Luke 5.12-16</a>)Den, wen Jesus kom dong fahn aafa di hilsaid, wan paila pipl wende fala im.
Aalava sodn wan man wid leprosy<RF q=+>Nuotis seh: Leprosy dah wehn wan bad skin siknis weh neva gat kyuor. kom op tu Jesus, chruo dong ihnself rait fronta im ahn seh, “Laad, if yuu waahn, yo kyan mek Ah get beta!”
So Jesus strech out ihn han, toch di man, ahn tel im seh, “Yees, Ah waahn kyuor yo, so get beta rait now!” Ahn siem taim di man wehn kyuor.
Den Jesus tel im seh, “Yo no fi tel nonbady bout dis; ongl go striet dah di Jewish priis ahn mek im saach yo. Mek shuor yo ker di aafrin gif weh Moses seh enybady weh get kyuor fi ker, fi shuo seh yu deh gud now.”
Wan govament ofishal shuo seh him gat plenty fiet<TS3>(<a href="tw://bible.*?42.7.1-10">Luke 7.1-10</a>)Wen Jesus gaan bak dah Capernaum, wan aamy aafisa —weh dah wehn di kyapm a wan hundred suoldya iina di Roman aamy— gaan tu im ahn beg im seh,
“Laad, mi sorvant deh dah mi huom deh lidong, bikaaz ihn kyaahn muuv ataal; ihn paralaiz ahn ihn gat plenty pien tu.”
Jesus tel im, “Ah gwain go ahn kyuor im.”
Bot di aamy aafisa ansa im seh, “Laad, Ah no gud nof fi yo kom iina mi hous. So, jos seh di wod ahn mi sorvant gwain get beta.
Ai nuo dis bikaaz Ai deh aanda mi sopierya dem, ahn Ai gat suoldya aanda mii tu. Ai ongl hafy tel wan a dem, ‘Go!’ ahn ihn go, or ‘Kom!’ ahn ihn kom. Ahn if Ah tel mi sorvant, ‘Du dis!’ ihn gwain du'ih.”
Fi chruut, plenty pipl weh dah no Jew gwain kom fahn iis ahn wes,<RF q=+>Or: “…gwain kom fahn aal uova…” ahn dehn gwain sidong fi iit wid fi wi ansesta Abraham, Isaac, ahn Jacob iina di Kingdom a Hevn.
Bot dem weh shuda bii paat a dat kingdom bot neva waahn pie main tu ihn wod gwain get chruo iina hel daaknis. Iina dah siem plies dehn gwain gat plenty halarin ahn di pipl dehn gwain grain dehn tiit jos sieka di pien weh dehn deh fiil.”
Den Jesus seh tu di aamy aafisa, “Golang! Bikaaz a di fiet weh yo gat, yo sorvant gwain get beta.”Ahn siem taim di aamy aafisa sorvant get beta!
Jesus kyuor plenty pipl dah Simon Peter hous<TS3>(<a href="tw://bible.*?41.1.29-34">Mark 1.29-34</a>; <a href="tw://bible.*?42.4.38-41">Luke 4.38-41</a>)Wen Jesus get dah Peter hous, ihn si Peter madanlaa deh lidong iina di bed, sik wid fiiva.
