Jesus tek out wan paila bad spirit outa two man<TS3>(<a href="tw://bible.*?41.5.1-20">Mark 5.1-20</a>; <a href="tw://bible.*?42.8.26-39">Luke 8.26-39</a>)Afta dat, dehn get dah di ada saida di liek weh paat di Garasenes pipl dem liv; ahn wen Jesus get outa di buot, ihn bok'op pan two man wid bad spirit weh wende kom outa di berin grong. Dehn wehn so mad nonbady kuda paas dehso.
