Bot wen di skai uova daak iina di maanin, unu seh, ‘Ih daak op, ahn gwain rien!’ Unu nuo how fi tel di weda bai deh luk pan di tingz dem weh hapm iina di skai, bot unu rifyuuz fi andastan di tingz dem weh shuo weh God deh du rait now.
Unu dah laik wan uova bad jinarieshan, weh on'fietful aal di taim, bikaaz unu kiip deh aks fi wan sain, bot unu no gwain si non sain ataal apaat fahn weh wehn hapm tu Jonah.”<RF q=+>Nuotis seh: Jonah dah wehn wan a di uol taim prafit weh wan big-big fish swala op, ahn ihn wehn iina di fish bely fi three diez ahn three nait, bifuor di fish spit'im op pahn wan sii shuor laiv.Den Jesus lef dem deh, ahn gaan weh.
Watch out fi di rilijos liida dehn bad influens<TS3>(<a href="tw://bible.*?41.8.14-21">Mark 8.14-21</a>)Wen ihn disaipl dehn get uova di ada saida di sii, dehn memba seh dehn neva bring muo bred.
