Dis dah weh God seh tu:“Laad, wen notn neva deh,dah yu wehn mek di ort ahn di hevnwid yo uon han dem.”
Aala demya tingz gwain kom tu wan en,bot yu gwain dedeh aal di taim.Demde tingz gwain wier outsiem laik uol kluoz.
